>Description:
Description of bug:
In the example document, the characters "a are interpreted
in the German language environment, but I expected them to
be handled in the English environment. In other words,
LaTeX prints
  ä
but I expected
  "a
in the output.

I am aware that resetting the language using groups
is not supposed to work in all circumstances, but this
particular behaviour is completely unexpected.


